name: R-13
description:
Debuted at this years Space City Con 2012. If you were unable to attend this years Con, here's your opportunity to get your signed autograph copy.

High quality Promo print  • Size: 11x17 • Signed by artist • Shipped in protective poly-sheets. 

R-13 is a graphic novel currently in production slated for a Fall 2013 release.

name: Las Locas #1
description:
They are beautiful, tough, and ultimately the most dangerous women on the planet. They are Las Locas!!! A organization of female bounty hunters with different talents, who roam the band lands of Texas and abroad taking out bad guys.

(Full color wrap-around cover with black and white interiors/ 40pages) The book is comprised of different short stories setup in a anthology format drawn by various artist from different parts of the world. This is the first installment of Las Locas issue 1.

name: Moe Art: Book One
description:
Maurice opens up his studio and displays a range of works showing promise of a artist on the move for bigger and unimaginable things.

In this first edition he reveals art works undiscovered, published and rejected works. As well as story concepts awaiting a breath of new air.

This collection of works is mainly a vault/library of visuals that is meant to inspire or motivate the creative process.

Publish Date: November 16,2010
Dimensions: Standard Portrait / Softcover
80 Pages
